.org/gnu/glibc/glibc-2.2.tar.gz","https://github.com/bminor/glibc/commit/2864e767053317538feafa815046fff89e5a16be#diff-94e8c502f255fdfc346df0e29fd4ef40","https://www.cee.studio/tdelete.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-2108","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-2108.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1593","title":"Microsoft Windows Internet Naming Service 域控制器重定向欺骗漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 的 Internet 名称服务（WINS）存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者可通过发送特殊的\"1Ch\"注册请求，诱使 WINS 将域控制器指向攻击者控制的恶意服务器。成功利用该漏洞可导致目标网络失去连接（拒绝服务），或通过域名解析劫持窃取域用户凭据。攻击无需身份认证，仅需向 WINS 服务发送特制注册包即可触发。该漏洞主要影响使用 WINS 的 Windows 域环境，当网络中仍在使用 Windows 95/98 客户端或主域控制器不可用时，其影响范围可能受到一定限制。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1593"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2009-01-15T01:30:00.407","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:47.633","remediation":"升级到已修复该问题的 Windows NT 4.0 SP6a 或 Windows 2000 SP2 及以上版本；在 WINS 服务中禁用对 1Ch（域控制器）NetBIOS 名称的远程动态注册，并配置仅允许受信任的域控制器进行名称注册；在边界防火墙限制 137/UDP、138/UDP、139/TCP 及 42/TCP 端口的外部访问，临时缓解来自不可信网络的 WINS 注册攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/1998-1999/msg00371.html","http://seclists.org/bugtraq/2001/Jan/0264.html","http://seclists.org/bugtraq/2001/Jan/0269.html","http://seclists.org/bugtraq/2001/Jan/0271.html","http://seclists.org/bugtraq/2001/Jan/0274.html","http://seclists.org/bugtraq/2001/Jan/0276.html","http://seclists.org/bugtraq/2001/Jan/0289.html","http://seclists.org/bugtraq/2001/Jan/0298.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/2221","https://www2.sans.org/reading_room/whitepapers/win2k/185.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a23c9152c0ce51f4625e88e1e6abe715ca2d7579/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1593.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1593","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1593.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2853180ecaf9d7461fd6bb98e4528ce223cae51d/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1593.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1ef90eac7bb1a353721fe038daf41872bdff01c4/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7p6m-p6r7-2f8p/GHSA-7p6m-p6r7-2f8p.json","https://github.com/kafti/svdb/blob/a5ddaa4d642610d7feb5ee694d65f7914256c2d8/svdb/vuln/print_cve_entry.py","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87947/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_114800_114900.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6f53fa07-a334-4387-b9db-ed00ba174a33.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1593.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-2108.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1180","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1180.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1557","title":"Ipswitch IMail 5.0 IMAP 服务器缓冲区溢出拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Ipswitch IMail 5.0 及更早版本的 IMAP 服务器（imapd）在处理登录功能时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。由于程序未对用户提交的用户名和密码长度进行有效校验，未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过发送超长的用户名或密码触发栈缓冲区溢出，导致 imapd 服务崩溃形成拒绝服务，并可能进一步执行任意代码。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，利用方式为向目标 IMAP 服务的登录接口发送特制超长字符串，危害等级中等，CVSS 评分 5.0。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1557"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2005-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:42.733","remediation":"升级 Ipswitch IMail 至 6.0 或更高版本，修复 imapd 登录模块对超长用户名及密码的缓冲区溢出缺陷。如暂无法升级，建议在防火墙层面限制 IMAP 服务仅对可信 IP 开放，并临时禁用外部 IMAP 访问作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92038879607336&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1895","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19377"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1180.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1090","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1090.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1374","title":"perlshop.cgi 购物车程序敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"perlshop.cgi 购物车程序存在敏感信息泄露漏洞，该程序将客户订单信息、信用卡号等敏感数据以文件形式存储在 Web 根目录下，未进行任何访问控制。远程攻击者只需通过 HTTP 请求直接访问这些文件路径即可获取客户敏感信息，导致用户隐私数据泄露。该漏洞影响使用 perlshop.cgi 的早期 Perl 购物车系统，攻击条件简单，无需身份认证。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1374"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2005-05-02T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.230","remediation":"立即将 perlshop.cgi 的数据存储目录移出 Web 根目录（如移至 /var/lib/perlshop/），并在 Web 服务器配置中禁止直接访问该目录（Apache 使用 <Directory> 指令或 .htaccess 的 Deny from all）。由于 perlshop.cgi 已长期无人维护，建议迁移至现代购物车系统（如 Magento、WooCommerce）并删除旧脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92523159819402&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1090.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1090.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1090.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1104","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1104.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1431","title":"Microsoft Zero Administration Kit (ZAK) 1.0 Office 97 后门访问漏洞","description":"Microsoft 零管理工具包 (ZAK) 1.0 及 Office 97 的 Appstation 模式存在策略绕过漏洞。攻击者可通过 Office 97 应用程序（如 Word）启动 Windows 资源管理器，将任意程序安装到临时目录并重命名为允许运行的应用程序名称（如 Winword.exe），从而绕过\"仅运行允许的应用程序\"安全策略。该漏洞影响安装了 ZAK 1.0 和 Office 97 的 Windows 系统，需要本地用户权限且能访问 Office 应用程序才可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，属中危本地权限提升漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1431"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2005-01-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:25.593","remediation":"立即卸载 Microsoft Zero Administration Kit (ZAK) 1.0 并删除相关注册表项，同时禁用 Office 97 的\"仅允许运行指定的应用程序\"策略，禁止通过 Office 应用程序启动 Explorer.exe，并清除TEMP目录中可疑的Winword.exe等文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91576100022688&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91606260910008&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/181","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19144","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0283d468fcc07a0a091bff7d6aca02552e8d0048/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1431.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1431","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1431.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2301e36f8af0694b1f220afdc97e9e07ee9e6a52/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1431.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q7hj-hx26-wwww/GHSA-q7hj-hx26-wwww.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1431.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_139200_139300.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4c7f1cef-cea9-488c-aedb-0aba038196cc.json","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1104.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1089","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1089.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1373","title":"FORE PowerHub 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FORE PowerHub 5.0.0 及更早版本存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 nmap 等工具发送特制的 TCP SYN 扫描包并结合 TCP/IP 操作系统指纹探测技术，导致目标设备响应异常并陷入挂起状态，无法正常提供服务。该漏洞影响 PowerHub 5.0.0 及之前版本，攻击者无需认证即可远程触发，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1373"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2005-01-05T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.090","remediation":"升级 FORE PowerHub 至 5.0.1 或更高版本以修复该拒绝服务漏洞。如无法升级，可在网络边界防火墙配置规则，限制对 PowerHub 管理端口的 SYN 扫描探测，或部署入侵检测系统拦截 nmap 等扫描工具的特征流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91651770130771&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1089.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1028","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1028.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1263","title":"Metamail 邮件处理程序任意文件写入漏洞","description":"Metamail 2.7-7.2 之前版本中存在任意文件写入漏洞。远程攻击者可通过发送包含 uuencode 编码附件的恶意邮件，在附件中指定目标文件的完整路径名，当 Metamail 脚本（如 sun-audio-file）调用 uuencode 处理该附件时，会将附件内容写入攻击者指定的任意路径，从而覆盖目标系统上的任意文件。该漏洞攻击条件简单，仅需向受害者发送特制邮件即可触发，危害较大。","severity":"LOW","score":2.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1263"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"2003-08-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:03.937","remediation":"升级 metamail 至 2.7-7.2 或更高版本（如 Debian 的 2.7-7.2 及以上软件包），通过系统包管理器执行 apt-get update && apt-get install metamail 或 yum update metamail 完成更新。如无法立即升级，可在邮件网关或 MTA 上禁用 uuencode 解码、过滤含 uuencoded 附件的邮件，并移除或重命名 /usr/bin/ 下 metamail 自带的 uuencode 相关脚本（如 sun-audio-file）以临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87773365324657&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1677","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1263","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1263.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xqm9-g4jx-xvgw/GHSA-xqm9-g4jx-xvgw.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1263.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_147200_147300.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--994159c6-4130-4132-93c9-332283f85f73.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--994159c6-4130-4132-93c9-332283f85f73.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1028.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1192","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1192.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1570","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9110,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10792}}","description":"OpenServer 5.0.5 系统中的 sar 命令（系统活动报告工具）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该漏洞位于 sar 处理命令行参数的代码中，当本地用户以超长字符串作为 -o 参数（指定输出文件）的值执行 sar 命令时，由于程序未对输入长度进行边界检查，导致缓冲区被溢出覆盖。攻击条件要求攻击者具备目标系统的本地登录权限（普通用户即可），无需远程网络访问。成功利用后，攻击者可通过精心构造的输入覆盖返回地址并执行任意代码，从而将权限提升至 root（超级用户），完全控制受影响的 OpenServer 5.0.5 主机。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1570"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2002-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:44.467","remediation":"建议立即安装 Caldera 发布的 CSSA-2002-SCO.17 安全补丁，升级系统自带的 sar 二进制文件至修复版本以消除缓冲区溢出漏洞。若无法立即应用补丁，可临时移除 /usr/bin/sar 的 SUID 权限或通过文件权限限制普通用户执行该命令，作为缓解措施降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=vuln-dev&m=102098949103708&w=2","http://online.securityfocus.com/archive/1/27074","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/8989.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/4089","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/35cd604fbbf2927fb6acbcd700e81d36cd6dec11/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1570.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1570","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-1570.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/3a7f9488e77673498ec37285be0a165ad71720f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1570.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/2a2be81fd4b47dc35d815a995b6429bd116a3b84/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-79g8-69hq-h5jh/GHSA-79g8-69hq-h5jh.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1570.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_148400_148500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000857.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--96c29d61-6975-4ef5-bc9c-437c88134827.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1192.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0934","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0934.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1091","title":"tin rtin UNIX新闻阅读器符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"UNIX 系统下的新闻阅读器 tin 和 rtin 在创建临时日志文件 /tmp/.tin_log 时使用了不安全的文件权限，并且程序会跟随符号链接进行操作。本地攻击者可通过预先创建符号链接指向目标文件，诱使程序以当前用户权限修改链接指向文件的权限，属于典型的符号链接攻击（symlink attack）。该漏洞影响多种 UNIX 发行版本，攻击者需要具有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低，可能造成敏感文件权限被非授权修改。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1091"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2002-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.177","remediation":"升级 tin 至 1.4 及以上版本，或 rtin 至更高版本，确保 /tmp/.tin_log 文件仅对当前用户可读写。如无法升级，可删除 /tmp/.tin_log 改为只读空文件并锁定权限，或使用 Sticky Bit 保护 /tmp 目录防止符号链接攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419835&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167419839&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=87602167420726&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/431","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/7481e97cf7b60a5b982d99d7dad1ea61174940fb/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1091","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/7cddb9480dac0125b9b2b00c91d6226d5d995ec7/1999/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/3508ccc52a2baed6a1946843005e8957c7067f39/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-10xx/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1091.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1091.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0934.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0926","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0926.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1081","title":"Novell Netware Web Server 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Novell WebServer Examples Toolkit 2 中的 files.pl 脚本存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求，利用该脚本对文件路径过滤不严的缺陷，读取服务器上任意文件，包括配置文件、密码文件等敏感信息。该漏洞影响 Novell NetWare Web Server 3.x 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。攻击者只需能够访问目标 Web 服务即可实施攻击，利用难度较低。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1081"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"2002-01-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:40.900","remediation":"升级 Novell NetWare Web Server 到不受影响的版本（NetWare 5 及以上）。如无法升级，立即从 Web 服务器目录中删除 `files.pl` 脚本文件，同时配置访问控制规则禁止外部访问 cgi-bin 目录下的未经授权脚本。在反向代理或 WAF 层面过滤包含 `..` 目录遍历特征的请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.roxanne.org/faqs/www-secure/wwwsf4.html#Q35","http://www.w3.org/Security/Faq/wwwsf8.html#Q87","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2054","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20482"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0926.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0926.toml"}]